					<div id="business-answers"><a href="/solutions" mce_href="/solutions"><img src="/userfiles/image/talent_based_solutions.png" mce_src="/userfiles/image/talent_based_solutions.png" border="0" style="border: 0;" mce_style="border: 0;"></a>
<p style="padding-left: 5px; width: 100%; text-align: left;"><br></p>
<p style="padding-left: 5px; width: 100%; text-align: left;">Talent Plus is the Leading Talent Assessment Partner℠ in the industry. Our structured interviews and assessments represent the core of our business and are essential to understanding talent. Talent Plus provides a scientific methodology to improve an organization’s culture one employee at a time. People are most effective when they can utilize their strengths to do work they enjoy. The talent identified in our assessments and person-to-person interviews is the basis for the talent-based development and solutions we bring to client organizations. Talent Plus works with successful global brands in a variety of industries – <a href="/healthcare" mce_href="/healthcare">health care</a>, <a href="/component/content/article/54-results/372-the-profit-of-retention-hospitality" mce_href="/component/content/article/54-results/372-the-profit-of-retention-hospitality" title="Hospitality">hospitality</a> and <a href="/results/69-talent-advantage?talent_advantage=retail" mce_href="/results/69-talent-advantage?talent_advantage=retail">retail</a>, as well as <a href="/results/69-talent-advantage?talent_advantage=automotive" mce_href="/results/69-talent-advantage?talent_advantage=automotive" title="Automotive">automotive</a>, consumer products, education, engineering, <a href="/results/69-talent-advantage?talent_advantage=financial" mce_href="/results/69-talent-advantage?talent_advantage=financial">financial</a>, <a href="/results/69-talent-advantage?talent_advantage=government" mce_href="/results/69-talent-advantage?talent_advantage=government">government</a>, manufacturing, ministry, not for profit, services and utility.</p>
<p style="padding-left: 5px; width: 100%; text-align: left;">The outcome? Engaged cultures and improved performance metrics.</p>
